                            Source
                        </span>
                            </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col order-2 order-md-1 col-12 col-md-6 justify-content-center  d-flex align-items-center ghwt" style="height:350px;font-size:22px">
            <h4>
                DogeWallet  help you manage your dogecoins  in the easiest way.
                We don't keep your private keys or your passwords or any data!
                Private keys are generated based on your password and pin.
                Create a strong password and pin and keep it in a safe place.
                If you lose your password and pin, you've lost funds in your account !
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col order-1 order-md-2 col-12 col-md-6 justify-content-center  d-flex align-items-center ghwt" style="height:350px;font-size:22px">
            <img src="~/imgs/doge1.png" style="height:150px;width:150px;" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

